{"tid":1663143,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"成個連登最濕鳩就係房屋台班柒頭","createTime":"2019-10-19T08:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T09:06:27.000Z","uid":39575,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e88b0f85a0b0dd53cc0550de42c2b5e8dfc56cf0","tid":1663143,"uid":39575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"入面完全係平行世界黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1c20c26fabb45b7edac2d4379ba66021a20539","tid":1663143,"uid":26952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"明天見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSJhsF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSJhsF.png&h=a75a6d4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a434d6b78bdaa5a2794564da2e5235c66474ac47","tid":1663143,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"陳帆：港鐵如不再受破壞一、兩周內可回復正常服務<br />\n咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c905fca0cbdd07ae86886f3ded3c327db1f0014","tid":1663143,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"e7bdd3d0edc0a176559e581657615b813b4e0f70","tid":1663143,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>全日 全民宣傳日</strong></span> <br />\n- 宣傳1020民陣大遊行<br />\n日期：10月20日<br />\n時間： 1330 <br />\n地點：梳士巴利花園<br />\n[ 各區宣傳，嗌口號，貼文宣，Airdrop ]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1900 - 2030 國際人道救援祈禱會</strong></span><br />\n- 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n[已獲不反對通知書]"},{"pid":"b82dc246444446ec69e3d306d58a7026112fcef2","tid":1663143,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d278aaaaf800e759742d76ee936cfeb6cd59ab35","tid":1663143,"uid":39575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82dc246444446ec69e3d306d58a7026112fcef2","tid":1663143,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}